[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/u-turn">U-turn</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>After making its attack, the user rushes back to switch places with a party Pokemon in waiting.</p>